Class User

java.lang.Object
app.model.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a user in the application. A user has a username, a collection of albums, and a list of user-specific tag types. This class is serializable to allow persistence.
Author:
Reuben Thomas, Ryan Zaken
